.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-CONFIG" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-config \- read or write CLN dynamic configuration
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-config get
.RI [ key ]
.br
.B lightning node-config set
.I key value
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reads or writes CLN dynamic configuration via
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR listconfigs
/
.BR setconfig .
Dynamic config changes take effect immediately without restarting the
daemon (CLN 23.08+).
.PP
.B get
prints all configs as JSON, or a single key's value if
.I key
is given.
.PP
.B set
updates a dynamic config value.  Only dynamically-reconfigurable keys
are accepted; the daemon enforces this.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success.
.TP
.B 5
Config key not found or setconfig failed.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-info (1),
.BR lightning-fee (1)
